Southern Cross May Announce Break-Up Plan This Week, Sky Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-10T20:23:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-10/southern-cross-may-announce-break-up-plan-this-week-sky-reports.html
Southern Cross Healthcare Plc may
announce that it intends to break itself up under a proposed
agreement with landlords this week, Sky News reported, citing an
unnamed person close to the situation. The break-up plans are
still in outline stage and will need the approval of investors
and creditors, Sky said, citing the person.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 